      <title>比特币的 Mt. Gox 悬而未决的问题让市场陷入悬念</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-s-lingering-mt-gox-overhang-leaves-market-in-a-state-of-anxiety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人们期待已久的 Mt.Gox 交易所破产，将分发价值约 80 亿美元的比特币，尽管这笔交易已经开始，但加密货币市场仍处于悬念状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-s-lingering-mt-gox-overhang-leaves-market-in-a-state-of-anxiety</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 20:54:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
